      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A crypto trading bot for Bybit & delta.exchange perpetuals. Reads market data on 4 timeframes, looks for an ICT-style setup (Inner Circle Trader methodology), and either alerts via Telegram or places real orders.",
