      "text": "1.  What is this bot?  (60 second version)",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 16,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.  What is this bot?  (60 second version)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "id7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 220,
      "width": 1160,
      "height": 179.0,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1796035740,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 300026768,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "It\u2019s a SCALPING BOT for crypto perpetuals (BTC/USDT, ETH/USDT, etc).\n\nIt does ONE thing on a 30-second loop:\n   1. Pull the latest price candles (4h, 15m, 3m, 1m) for each pair.\n   2. Run them through an ICT-style checklist of 4 conditions.\n   3. If ALL 4 light up \u2192 call it a BUY or SELL, alert Telegram, and (if live mode is on) place a real order with SL + TP attached.\n   4. Otherwise \u2192 record it as a \u201cnear miss\u201d and try again next loop.\n\nStatus today: SIGNAL-ONLY by default. Live trading is gated behind ENABLE_LIVE_TRADING + LIVE_ALLOWED_PAIRS + a paper-trade gate (ADR-0005).\nYou also get a Streamlit dashboard (visual debugger) and a backtest engine (replay history through the same brain).",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "It\u2019s a SCALPING BOT for crypto perpetuals (BTC/USDT, ETH/USDT, etc).\n\nIt does ONE thing on a 30-second loop:\n   1. Pull the latest price candles (4h, 15m, 3m, 1m) for each pair.\n   2. Run them through an ICT-style checklist of 4 conditions.\n   3. If ALL 4 light up \u2192 call it a BUY or SELL, alert Telegram, and (if live mode is on) place a real order with SL + TP attached.\n   4. Otherwise \u2192 record it as a \u201cnear miss\u201d and try again next loop.\n\nStatus today: SIGNAL-ONLY by default. Live trading is gated behind ENABLE_LIVE_TRADING + LIVE_ALLOWED_PAIRS + a paper-trade gate (ADR-0005).\nYou also get a Streamlit dashboard (visual debugger) and a backtest engine (replay history through the same brain).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
