      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Fibonacci 50% level inside the OB range.\nPRICE > FIB 50%  \u2192 PREMIUM (only sell)\nPRICE < FIB 50%  \u2192 DISCOUNT (only buy)\nFilters trades to the right half of\nthe range \u2014 NOT in current code.",
