      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Source of truth for canonical rules: user notes on the shared Excalidraw. Use this as a punch-list when validating a strategy run \u2014 every  GAP / WRONG  row is a place the executor will lie to you about being \u201ccorrect\u201d.",
