      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ROBUSTNESS GATE  \u2192  before flipping ENABLE_LIVE_TRADING, every  WRONG / GAP / PARTIAL  row above must turn  PASS  (or be explicitly waived in an ADR). This card is the diagram\u2019s job: stop the strategy from claiming it\u2019s executable when it isn\u2019t.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
