      "text": "Rahul_ideation/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 .env                                  secrets + ENABLE_LIVE_TRADING flag\n\u2502\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 data/                                 (all gitignored)\n    \u251c\u2500\u2500 cache/                            parquet OHLCV cache (re-fetchable)\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 bybit/BTC_USDT_USDT/\n    \u2502       \u251c\u2500\u2500 1m.parquet \u00b7 3m.parquet \u00b7 15m.parquet \u00b7 4h.parquet\n    \u2502\n    \u251c\u2500\u2500 journal/\n    \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 signals.json                  every BUY/SELL ever fired (THE LEDGER)\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 last_signal.json              {pair}_{direction} \u2014 Telegram dedup\n    \u2502\n    \u251c\u2500\u2500 runs/\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 backtest_curve.json           equity curve consumed by the dashboard\n    \u2502\n    \u251c\u2500\u2500 logs/\n    \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 scanner.log                   plain text (WARNING+)\n    \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 scanner.json.log              structured JSON (INFO+)\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 *.json.log                    one per get_json_logger(name)\n    \u2502\n    \u2514\u2500\u2500 KILL_SWITCH_ENGAGED               sentinel file (presence = halt)\n                                          written by runtime.kill_switch.engage()",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Rahul_ideation/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 .env                                  secrets + ENABLE_LIVE_TRADING flag\n\u2502\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 data/                                 (all gitignored)\n    \u251c\u2500\u2500 cache/                            parquet OHLCV cache (re-fetchable)\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 bybit/BTC_USDT_USDT/\n    \u2502       \u251c\u2500\u2500 1m.parquet \u00b7 3m.parquet \u00b7 15m.parquet \u00b7 4h.parquet\n    \u2502\n    \u251c\u2500\u2500 journal/\n    \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 signals.json                  every BUY/SELL ever fired (THE LEDGER)\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 last_signal.json              {pair}_{direction} \u2014 Telegram dedup\n    \u2502\n    \u251c\u2500\u2500 runs/\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 backtest_curve.json           equity curve consumed by the dashboard\n    \u2502\n    \u251c\u2500\u2500 logs/\n    \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 scanner.log                   plain text (WARNING+)\n    \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 scanner.json.log              structured JSON (INFO+)\n    \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 *.json.log                    one per get_json_logger(name)\n    \u2502\n    \u2514\u2500\u2500 KILL_SWITCH_ENGAGED               sentinel file (presence = halt)\n                                          written by runtime.kill_switch.engage()",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
